  "description": "A stunning nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated with lights, featuring a vibrant fireworks display above a long bridge. The bridge, spanning dark water, is lit with numerous white lights, creating a striking linear pattern. In the background, a dense urban landscape rises, punctuated by tall buildings with glowing windows. A burst of fireworks explodes in the sky, displaying a dazzling array of red, white, and golden sparks. Another, smaller fireworks burst is visible adjacent. The overall scene suggests a festive occasion or celebration within a large metropolitan area.",
